Text: brodahisou, thanks for all the Frazetta torrents, even though it might have been the news of his passing away that inspired you...

Thanks ajones81

The Frank Frazetta Image Comics Collection is something that I've been working on for a while, but got side-lined by other projects.  With the sad news of Frazetta passing away I thought that it would be a suitable tribute for him, at least in the scanning and torrenting world.

The other Frazetta torrents I had uploaded before at Z-Cult FM before its demise.
